DELETAR COLLECITON INTEIRA (os documents no interior) --> 







db.collectionName.deleteMany({})













DROPPAR A COLLECTION:







db.collection.drop()

















-> DROPPAR __ A DATABASE --> é 



'db.dropDatabase()'....











--> PARA DELETAR A COLLECTION, use 


'db.collection.drop()'....